{"type":null,"faqId":34824,"title":"How do I enter recovery mode and restore my phone to its factory settings?","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<a name=\"_Toc393102032\"><span>When an update package is available on your microSD card or the download for an online update is complete, with the phone off, press and hold the power and volume up keys to enter recovery mode. In recovery mode, you can press the volume keys to select the desired option. Then, </span><span>touch</span><span> the menu key to enable a specific function. </span></a>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<a name=\"_Toc394678935\"><span>To restore your phone to its factory settings, touch </span><span class=\"s1\">Settings</span><span> &gt; </span><span class=\"s1\">Backup &amp; reset</span><span> &gt; </span><span class=\"s1\">Factory data reset</span><span>.</span></a><span> </span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=110931\" style=\"width:1.6868056in;height:2.9993055in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=110932\" style=\"width:1.6868056in;height:2.9993055in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":244,"languageName":"mm","faqCode":"9564","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436871815000,"seriesProductName":"H30-L02","visitedTimes":7,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"HONOR 3C LTE (H30-L02)","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}